org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd

Class CDFONTTABLE.CDFACE

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.AbstractStruct
      • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.cd.CDFONTTABLE.CDFACE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    CDFONTTABLE

    public static class CDFONTTABLE.CDFACE
extends AbstractStruct
    This defines part of the structure of a font table item in a note. A font table item in a note allows rich text in the note to be displayed using fonts other than those defined in FONT_FACE_xxx. (editods.h)
